2588:MyHardWare/Src/sdio_sd.c ****   * @brief  Enables or disables the SDIO wide bus mode.
2589:MyHardWare/Src/sdio_sd.c ****   * @param  NewState: new state of the SDIO wide bus mode.
2590:MyHardWare/Src/sdio_sd.c ****   *   This parameter can be: ENABLE or DISABLE.
2591:MyHardWare/Src/sdio_sd.c ****   * @retval SD_Error: SD Card Error code.
